*Kompanija* je obezbedila novac za pokretanje projekta. (The company provided money to start the project.) 

Oni su zajedno sa *kompanijom* osnovali fond za decu. (They established a fund for children together with the company.)

Preneti smo od *kompanije* da će nam obezbediti nove mašine. (We were informed by the company that they will provide us with new machines.)

On je zaposlen u *kompaniji* koja se bavi proizvodnjom. (He is employed in a company that deals with production.)

*Kompanija* je uspešno izvršila posao. (The company successfully completed the job.)